### Send XML Person through the Camel pipeline (-> Kafka -> /quarkus/hello)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/data
Content-Type: application/xml

<person>
    <name>Alice Smith</name>
    <birthday>1990-06-15</birthday>
</person>

###

### Send another person through the pipeline
POST http://localhost:8080/api/data
Content-Type: application/xml

<person>
    <name>Bob Johnson</name>
    <birthday>1985-03-22</birthday>
</person>

###

### Call the Quarkus receiver endpoint directly (mocks a downstream application)
POST http://localhost:8080/quarkus/hello
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Carol White",
  "birthday": "1995-11-30"
}
